{"tid":1610522,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"10月2日 國際非暴力日","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:29:20.000Z","uid":189077,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8b2c4388670f1a32e7b5d74b151a4201d90448","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:54:43.000Z","msg":"國際非暴力日即每年10月2日，聖雄甘地的生日。<br />\n2007年聯合國大會通過決議以聖雄甘地的生日訂立為國際非暴力日。目的是希望各國反對任何的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n我地聽晚做和理非去港島，係和平記念碑集合。"},{"pid":"faaa439ad8b5495746b35a26786a01f285ad4712","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"自推5次，無人理就算。<br />\n1"},{"pid":"aac4253dc300865d0290b82f4f84f74bfb4a73e5","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:56:09.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b3d19918ff7f894eef465b0d38beca39f27d20","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:57:16.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6d73be5c668176fb8fa61ff4dcf58adf66e320","tid":1610522,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"請全民無&middot;限&middot;期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"1f3bfb676a2c77c6a306f172985c451b8d511a2b","tid":1610522,"uid":134840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038c4dc9e2e1f6868a322b59d977d932160e9d5a","tid":1610522,"uid":214192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"仲有時間吹雞，國際非暴力日啱曬我地輸出警暴 制度暴力呢啲嘢"},{"pid":"7bcb238a12ce961a63e58be3c98989e5fef26919","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"10月2日1924年：國際聯盟簽訂《日內瓦議定書》。<br />\n《禁止在戰爭中使用窒息性、毒性或其他氣體和細菌作戰方法的議定書》（法語：Protocole concernant la prohibition d'emploi &agrave; la guerre de gaz asphyxiants, toxiques ou similaires et de moyens bact&eacute;riologiques; 英語：Protocol for the Prohibition of the Use in War of Asphyxiating, Poisonous or other Gases, and of Bacteriological Methods of Warfare），簡稱《日內瓦議定書》（法語：Protocole de Gen&egrave;ve; 英語：Geneva Protocol），各締約國同意在戰爭中不使用窒息性、毒性或其他氣體，以及使用一切類似的液體、物體或器件，即化學武器與生物武器[1]。締約國於1925年6月17日在瑞士日內瓦簽署了該協議，於1928年2月8日開始生效。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗議POPO射過期蛋</span></strong>"},{"pid":"93ba2c149f5e40d1fdc113176e9944ea2befba16","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:34.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5598839c934d6ca4805623b6c6b0b53836c071f","tid":1610522,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"10.2 非暴力日？ 依家清緊場喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baee9088c0c2467b873042456e35dd158b6097e4","tid":1610522,"uid":189077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5598839c934d6ca4805623b6c6b0b53836c071f","tid":1610522,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci